author: chirino
msg: Fix for AMQ-4563: Changes the KahaDB store to use a more consistent key for message ids.  MessageId.toString can change depending on how the message was encoded.
Support storing the externally generated message id of a message in the MessageID class so that Selectors can operate against that external message id.
